Package com.google.publicalerts.cap.feed

This package contains classes to parse and write feeds (Atom, RSS, and more) enclosing CAP messages.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
CapFeedParser Parses feeds of alerts, the entries in those feeds, and the CAP alerts in those entries.
CapFeedValidator Validates portions of Atom/RSS feeds (fat or thin) of CAP alerts beyond what is done in by the schemas in CapFeedParser.
 

Enum Summary
CapFeedException.FeedErrorType Types of errors that can occur when validating a feed.
CapFeedException.FeedRecommendationType Recommendations for improving the utility of a feed.
 

Exception Summary
CapFeedException An exception for CAP feeds.
 

Package com.google.publicalerts.cap.feed Description

This package contains classes to parse and write feeds (Atom, RSS, and more) enclosing CAP messages. Currently Atom and RSS are supported.
